title: Jurm
subTitle: SHEKHAR IS A POLICE OFFICER IN THE BOMBAY POLICE FORCE. HE IS A HONEST AND DEDICATED MAN MARRIED TO MEENA FROM HER A DAUGHTER BABLI- THEY MAKE AN ENVIABLE FAMILY. KADAM, HIS JUNIOR OFFICER IS THE ONLY REAL FRIEND HE HAS. ALL IS WELL WITH SHEKHAR AND THEN SUDDENLY ONE DAY HIS LIFE BEGINS TO FALL APRT. EDITOR RITESH NANDY IS KILLED.

title: Prem Deewane
subTitle: A young couple in love run away together after their parents oppose their relationship. They are misguided into kidnapping a wealthy person for a big ransom by a shrewd uncle who has his own agenda.

title: Police Aur Mujrim
subTitle: After DSP Vishal arrests two thugs, their boss kidnaps the commissioner's daughter. But after Vishal rescues the girl and jails the thugs, they return to hurt Vishal and the commissioner's families.

title: Sanam
subTitle: Amid the grim shadows of cross-border terrorism in India, love shines bright, guiding troubled army man Gaurav and village belle Sanam towards each other.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.

title: Hamara Dil Aapke Paas Hai
subTitle: When Preeti stands up against a murderer in court, she suffers a devastating consequence. Later, after being rejected by her loved ones, she finds shelter and support in an empathetic stranger.

title: Jaanwar
subTitle: A criminal changes the course of his life when he decides to raise a baby who has survived a train crash, but chaos ensues when his past begins to haunt him.

title: Mr. & Mrs. Khiladi
subTitle: When stars misalign, love blossoms between an astrology-obsessed idler and a headstrong fish heiress whose father will settle for nothing less than a hardworking son-in-law.

title: Tirangaa
subTitle: Brigadier Suryadev Singh and Shivajirao Waghle, a police inspector, work together to track down a terrorist who plans to evade India.

title: Daanveer
subTitle: Vijay, an orphan, is tasked with raising his siblings, Vishal and Sudha. Later, Sudha is disowned by her in-laws and Vishal falls for the enemy's daughter but Vijay comes to their rescue.

title: Daanveer
subTitle: Vijay, an orphan, is tasked with raising his siblings, Vishal and Sudha. Later, Sudha is disowned by her in-laws and Vishal falls for the enemy's daughter but Vijay comes to their rescue.

title: Barsaat
subTitle: An automobile designer, Arav, goes to the US for his job and falls in love with Anna. But just as they are about to be wed, he is forced to return to his wife in India when his father falls sick.

title: Sahebzaade
subTitle: Amid the hills, two brothers raised by their mother fall for the same woman, unearthing secrets that test their loyalty and force them to confront a shadow from the past.

title: Moksha
subTitle: Vikram and Ritika plan to rob a bank to fund their business of providing free legal services to impoverished people. However, things get complicated when she is found dead.

title: Jodi No. 1
subTitle: Two friends, Jai and Veeru hatch a clever plot to deceive Rai Bahadur and rob him. However, their plans take an unexpected turn when they fall in love with Rai Bahadur's daughters.

title: Saajan Chale Sasural
subTitle: After Shyamsunder presumes that his first wife Pooja died in a flood, he marries Divya. When he learns that Pooja is alive, he has to juggle between his wives, keeping both his marriages a secret.

title: Nadiya Ke Paar
subTitle: Chandan, a farmer's nephew, is in love with Gunja, his sister-in-law's sibling. However, when her sister dies in an accident, Gunja is expected to marry Chandan's brother.

title: Jigar
subTitle: Duryodhan, a wrestler, is Raju's friend, but due to a misunderstanding he rapes and kills Raju's sister. Raju later seeks Baba Thakur's help to train in fighting to avenge his sister's death.

title: Ram Teri Ganga Maili
subTitle: When Ganga's husband abandons her, she embarks on a journey to Calcutta to find him and ensure her son has a better future. But she is cheated and forced to work in a brothel.

title: Sheshnaag
subTitle: Pritam and Banu, two shape-shifting snakes in human form, seek protection from a young man when an evil priest tries to hunt them down and use them in a ritual for wealth and immortality.

title: Sheshnaag

title: Bomb Blast
subTitle: Jai Kishen is an aspiring police officer who marries his girlfriend against his parents' wishes. Meanwhile, MLA Sadakhare hires a few men to carry out a bomb blast.

title: Insaaf: The Final Justice
subTitle: When a witness is killed, a truthful police officer embarks on a mission to catch the culprit and uncovers a terrifying truth.

title: Awarapan
subTitle: A hitman sets out to rescue his boss's mistress and send her back to her boyfriend after learning that she is a victim of sex trafficking.

title: Kyon Ki
subTitle: In the chaotic environment of a faraway psychiatric hospital, love blossoms between a closed-off doctor and a rebellious patient with a troubled past.

title: Kohram
subTitle: Colonel Balbir Singh Sodhi assumes a disguise to unveil the true colours of Veer Bhadra Singh, a corrupt minister. Soon, Major Ajit teams up with him to execute the mission.

title: The Hero: Love Story of a Spy
subTitle: Arun Khanna, an Indian spy, collaborates with Reshma to stop a nuclear attack. However, Reshma's identity is compromised during her undercover mission in Pakistan.

title: Zakhmi Sipahi
subTitle: Shakti is an honest police officer out to avenge the death of his father. He faces many trials and tribulations in his journey towards fulfilling this task.

title: Indian
subTitle: Police officer Raj Azad arrests terrorist Wasim Khan and prepares to interrogate him. However, his father-in-law mysteriously dies, after which he is blamed for his death and goes on the run.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.
